OL,3,CNight buses to be rolled out across
OL,4,CGreater Manchester
OL,6,FWith one month to go until the Bee
OL,7,FNetwork rolls out in Oldham, Rochdale,
OL,8,Fparts of Bury and Manchester, Mayor of
OL,9,FGreater Manchester Andy Burnham is set
OL,10,Fto reveal important details about this
OL,11,Fnext phase.
OL,13,Fand means the region now has publicly-
OL,14,Fcontrolled bus services for the first
OL,15,Ftime since the 1980s when services
OL,16,Fwere deregulated everywhere outside
OL,17,FLondon.
