OL,3,CNight buses to be rolled out across
OL,4,CGreater Manchester
OL,6,FIt is a long term plan to join up bus,
OL,7,Ftram and train services, giving people
OL,8,Fone joined up transport network, like
OL,9,FLondon, where one ticket can be used
OL,10,Fon multiple modes of transport.
OL,12,FThe first phase in September saw 50
OL,13,Fnew electric buses launched in Bolton,
OL,14,FWigan and parts of Salford and Bury.
OL,16,FThe Metrolink tram service is part of
OL,17,Fthe Bee Network, with 99 stops and a
OL,18,Fnetwork of lines across Greater
OL,19,FManchester.
