OL,6,FBee Network bus services will be
OL,7,Fplanned to link up with Metrolink,
OL,8,Flocal rail and the cycling and walking
OL,9,Fnetwork.
OL,11,FRail services will join the network in
OL,12,F2030.
OL,14,FThere are also ideas for an
OL,15,Funderground and tram-train services,
OL,16,Fwhere Metrolink can run on the same
OL,17,Flines as trains.
