OL,3,CNight buses to be rolled out across
OL,4,CGreater Manchester
OL,6,FEarlier this month it was confirmed
OL,7,Fnight buses are set to arrive in parts
OL,8,Fof Greater Manchester this year, with
OL,9,Fplans for a trial being finalised by
OL,10,FTransport for Greater Manchester.
OL,12,FSome night buses already run in the
OL,13,Fregion, largely south Manchester, but
OL,14,Fthe new plans would see them operate
OL,15,Fin areas where Bee Network buses are
OL,16,Fcurrently in operation, namely Wigan
OL,17,Fand Bolton and parts of Bury, Salford
OL,18,Fand Manchester.
