OL,3,CNight buses to be rolled out across
OL,4,CGreater Manchester
OL,6,FIt is hoped that the night buses will
OL,7,Fbe a boost to Greater Manchester's
OL,8,Fnight time economy.
OL,10,FThe Bee Network being under public
OL,11,Fownership means the Greater Manchester
OL,12,FCombined Authority has more control
OL,13,Fover fares, timetables and routes by
OL,14,Fissuing franchises to private firms to
OL,15,Foperate services.
OL,17,FThe public will have the power to pass
OL,18,Fcomment and rate journeys, which will
OL,19,Faffect the financial contracts.
