OL,3,CNight buses to be rolled out across
OL,4,CGreater Manchester
OL,6,FOn 24 March 2024 the second phase of
OL,7,Fbus franchising in Greater Manchester
OL,8,Fwill roll out in Oldham, Rochdale and
OL,9,Fparts of Bury and Manchester,
OL,10,Ffollowing the launch of the Bee
OL,11,FNetwork in September 2023.
OL,13,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,14,FBurnham, Transport Commissioner Vernon
OL,15,FEveritt and Leader of Bury Council,
OL,16,FEamonn O'Brien will be giving
OL,17,Fimportant updates about the new roll
OL,18,Fout on Monday 19 February.
